Cambridge, Massachusetts.

00:00:09.810 --> 00:00:13.280
Today, it's my great pleasure
to introduce one of the most

00:00:13.280 --> 00:00:16.130
interesting and successful
people I know,

00:00:16.130 --> 00:00:18.540
