00:00:26.850 --> 00:00:30.747
"Prime Time," "Face Time," "Air
Time," "Drive Time," and

00:00:30.747 --> 00:00:34.210
now "The Other Woman," which
is front of you, her first

00:00:34.210 --> 00:00:38.407
recent hardcover, which went
back for a second printing, I

00:00:38.407 --> 00:00:39.186
think, the first week.

00:00:39.186 --> 00:00:42.000
So it's been highly
successful.

